## Key Settings (TreeMemoryMinigame Inspector)
| Field | Default | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| `gridSize` | 5 | Grid is gridSize × gridSize |
| `tileSpacing` | 1.2 | World units between tile centers |
| `showPatternDuration` | 2.5s | How long the pattern is visible |
| `resultDisplayDuration` | 1.2s | Pause after each round result before next round |

