## Key Technical Notes
- URP — use **Sprite-Lit-Default** shader, not Sprites/Default
- New Input System — `OnMouseDown` doesn't work. **Physics2DRaycaster** on camera is mandatory
- `TreeMemoryMinigame` inherits `MinigameResult` — never call `Succeed()`/`Fail()` directly, always goes through `MinigameBridge`
- `ForestFireBridge` defaults to 0 uncontained fires if Forest Fire Fighting was not played — minigame is fully playable standalone at minimum difficulty
- Players cannot deselect tiles once clicked — intentional
- Pattern is re-randomized each round (does not build on previous round's pattern)

